	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have played all the Int. caster classes except the magician thus far. Wizards are fun but no soloing there, necros can solo but it gets old building faction just to bank. Enchanters are ok, but what can I say....I like to blow stuff up.<br><br>So, after talking to some people I have decided to give a magician a try. Here is my question.....if I were to raise about 3k to build a magician what kinds of things might I purchase to help me on my way. I know that Intelligence jewelry is a given to get, but what kind of items will be helpful?<br><br><br>Let me know,<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Zepha Mercyheal <br>Cleric 40<br>Lords of Mischief<br>Luclin Server</td></tr>
