<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101484522113846></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101484522113846><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=101484522113846>Twink Stuff</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=101484522113846#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=143930><span id=Scholar>SemiMaster</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>20 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Feb 27th 4:27 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.06]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Elemental Binder: Hehe, what can i say, people GIVE these away, if not away, for like 50pp max<br>Thats a cheap 5 int and some resists right off the bat.<br><br>Earrings: Prob black sapphire ones or two bat skull earrings, pretty cheap now adays<br><br>Rings:Ring of frost and a silver quartz one, or maybe two moonstone rings<br><br>Robe:Crystaline robes 300pp or less on my server, maybe more or less on luclin, im not sure. Or a green silken drape for 100pp or less<br><br>Arms:Gatorscale for a 4 int boost<br><br>Wrist: Bracelet of woven grass(2 of them) or a two polished bone bracelets.<br><br>Neck: Petrified Erudite Heart ammy, i got mine for 100 for 5 int 15 mana and 10 svm, i think the person was not paying attention at the time<br><br>Dusty blood stained gloves +25 mana<br><br>Stein of Moggok for sure and when you get a pet, use a Tome with Silver runes, until then, go hunt ulthorks to get an ulthork tusk for melee in the early levels.<br>Or maybe a sacraficial dagger<br><br>Kunzar cloak or cloak of the rygorr oracles would be a good back<br><br>Legs and belts and shoulders are rather expensive at this time, but i guess silversilk leggings for 4 agi and 12 hp wouldn't be too bad for 25pp.<br>Crystaline belts are good, but for a 3 int 20 mana 20 hp belt, thats gonna run about 500pp or more i would say<br><br>Boots are expensive for int, so i'd just get kobold hide boots until gebs or crystaline slippers or netted kelp shoes.<br><br>Focus items are cool, its just i haven't found any of the pieces to quest it yet.<br><br>With 3k you should be off to a good start<br><br>Kaeci lvl 24 Mage of The Rathe<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
