	   <tr><td colspan=2>You don't get anything back from a pet, no matter how nicely you beg.<br><br>There are TONS of summoned items to give a pet, including the armor, which does increase its armor class(as a precaution, DON'T put anything in that summoned bag unless you want to lose it when you log off or go linkdead).<br><br>Kajaina Lvl 43 Druid of The Rathe<br>Kaeci Lvl 23 Magician of The Rathe<br><br>Note: Fire pet with two summoned sword of runes and a full set of summoned armor lasts as long as a water pet, and with a water pet it lasts about as long as an earth pet.<br>2nd Note: Air pets, well suck unless you are fighting a caster, stick with earth or water for soloing(water pets are my favorite cuz of regen and no poison and they have overall best stats)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
